{"atom_id": "md_dmFT_ex_a014", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "file": "knowledge_base/domains/FT/examples.md", "line_start": 22, "line_end": 22, "verbatim": "The suppft.xpt dataset represents that the subject used a cane while performing the 6 Minute Walk Test. In this example, FTGRPID is used to link this SUPPFT record to the 6 result records in FT. FTGRPID groups the FT records together by FTCAT and VISITNUM for an USUBJID.", "parent_section": "§FT.1 [Example 1]", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "general-purpose", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_md_v1.9.1", "ts": "2026-05-06T09:00:00Z"}}
